data.description: Spacious 4 bed 2.5 bath home in amazing like new condition!  Stone faced fireplace in family room. Formal dining room, eat in kitchen with breakfast nook & pantry.  All appliances are in like new condition. Huge master suite complete with walk in closet & Jacuzzi tub. Large bedrooms with ample closet space. Laundry on 2nd floor. Forced hot air & central a/c. Second floor family room is great for kids. Oversized rear deck perfect for entertaining. Built in 2 car garage. Commuter location only 5 min to major highways & shopping.
